cm-gotoparent-tooltip:
Text of the tooltip for the {{msg-wm|Convenient-discussions-cm-gotoparent}} item of the comment menu. When you click the item, it sends you to the parent comment of the current comment.

See also:
* {{msg-wm|Convenient-discussions-cm-gotochild-tooltip}}

cm-gotochild-tooltip:
Text of the tooltip for the {{msg-wm|Convenient-discussions-cm-gotochild}} item of the comment menu. The item appears in the parent comment menu after you click the {{msg-wm|Convenient-discussions-cm-gotoparent}} item of the child comment menu. When you click the item, it sends you back to that child comment.

See also:
* {{msg-wm|Convenient-discussions-cm-gotoparent-tooltip}}

